Hello Andrew,

If I set api_level to 23, it fails because my SDK is level 24. It gives:
ERROR: missing input file '@androidsdk//:platforms/android-23/android.jar'.
ERROR: /home/sander/tensorflow/tensorflow/examples/android/BUILD:47:1: //tensorflow/examples/android:tensorflow_demo: missing input file '@androidsdk//:platforms/android-23/android.jar'.

I included the output file of the original error I got when running with api_level 24.

Could it be possible that the demo only works with SDK 23?

Thanks for your time!
